title_bed_bats_review: Hotel in Cox's Bazar · 1 bedroom · 2 beds · 1 private bath
listing_description:
Hotel The Cox Today is a privately owned 5 Star Standard Luxury Hotel in Cox's Bazar, Bangladesh. It is situated in an attractive location of Kolatoli Road, Cox's Bazar which is only 5 minutes drive form the Cox's Bazar Airport. It is a place of choice of most of the corporate executives, foreigners,  and for those who prefer to stay in luxury with stunning view of The 'Bay of Bengal'.
Complimentary: buffet breakfast, swimming pool, gym and airport pick-up & drop service.

title_bed_bats_review: Boutique hotel in Cox's Bazar · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 private bath
listing_description: Enjoy the glamour of this stylish, upscale place in Cox's Bazar, ideal for a couple with a complimentary breakfast. You will get honeymoon room decoration & candle lite dinner here. Our place is just adjacent to the Sugondha Sea Beach of Cox's Bazar, only a 5 min walking distance. Enjoy the World's largest unbroken sandy sea beach, the largest marine drive in the world and Buddhist monastery, and many more in Cox's Bazar.

listing_description: You'll enjoy your time at this cheerful getaway in Cox's Bazar. Enjoy easy access to popular tourist destinations and restaurants from this charming place to stay.
